            <h4 class="docs-h4">Hvad sker der trin for trin?</h4>
            <div class="docs-sequence">
                <div class="docs-seq-step">
                    <div class="docs-seq-num">1</div>
                    <div class="docs-seq-content">
                        <div class="docs-seq-actor">Bruger</div>
                        <div class="docs-seq-action">Starter Blazor-appen med <code>dotnet run</code>. Ingen MCP-server k&oslash;rer endnu.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="docs-seq-step">
                    <div class="docs-seq-num">2</div>
                    <div class="docs-seq-content">
                        <div class="docs-seq-actor">Bruger</div>
