                    <div class="docs-seq-content">
                        <div class="docs-seq-actor">Blazor</div>
                        <div class="docs-seq-action"><code>McpBridgeService.ConnectAsync()</code> starter en <strong>ny Node.js child-process</strong>: <code>npx -y @@nabsolutions/nab-al-tools-mcp</code></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="docs-seq-step">
                    <div class="docs-seq-num">4</div>
