            @* ─── Initialization Guard ─── *@
            <h3 class="docs-h3">Initialisering &mdash; det f&oslash;rste der sker</h3>
            <p class="docs-section-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                F&oslash;r noget andet kan ske, <strong>skal</strong> AI'en kalde <code>initialize</code>-v&aelig;rkt&oslash;jet.
                Det fortæller serveren hvilket AL-projekt den skal arbejde med.
            </p>

            <div class="docs-flow">
                <div class="docs-flow-step">
                    <div class="docs-flow-num"><span>1</span></div>
                    <div class="docs-flow-line"></div>
                    <div class="docs-flow-body">
                        <h4>AI kalder <code>initialize</code></h4>
                        <p>Sender stien til AL-app-mappen (der hvor <code>app.json</code> ligger) og eventuelt en workspace-fil.</p>
                        <div class="docs-code-block" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
                            <div class="docs-code-title">Eksempel: initialize-kald</div>
                            <pre><code>{
  <span class="cf">"appFolderPath"</span>: <span class="cs">"C:/dev/MyApp"</span>,
  <span class="cf">"workspaceFilePath"</span>: <span class="cs">"C:/dev/MyApp.code-workspace"</span>
}</code></pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="docs-flow-step">
                    <div class="docs-flow-num"><span>2</span></div>
                    <div class="docs-flow-line"></div>
                    <div class="docs-flow-body">
                        <h4>Serveren validerer og indl&aelig;ser</h4>
                        <p>Loader <code>app.json</code> (manifest), projektindstillinger, og finder den genererede <code>g.xlf</code>-masterfil i <code>Translations/</code>-mappen. Fejler hvis filen ikke findes (projektet skal v&aelig;re bygget f&oslash;rst).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="docs-flow-step">
                    <div class="docs-flow-num"><span>3</span></div>
                    <div class="docs-flow-line last"></div>
                    <div class="docs-flow-body">
                        <h4>Global state gemmes</h4>
                        <p>Serveren gemmer indstillinger, manifest og g.xlf-sti i hukommelsen. Alle efterf&oslash;lgende tool-kald genbruger denne state. Det er derfor initialisering kun skal ske &eacute;n gang per session.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="docs-callout">
                <strong>Guard pattern:</strong> Hvert tool (undtagen <code>initialize</code>) starter med at tjekke:
                "Er serveren initialiseret?" Hvis nej, returneres en fejl der fort&aelig;ller AI'en at den skal kalde <code>initialize</code> f&oslash;rst.
                Det sikrer at AI'en aldrig kan lave fejl ved at kalde v&aelig;rkt&oslash;jer uden kontekst.
            </div>

            @* ─── Hvert tool i detaljer ─── *@
            <h3 class="docs-h3">Hvert v&aelig;rkt&oslash;j i detaljer</h3>
            <p class="docs-section-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                Her er pr&aelig;cis hvad hvert v&aelig;rkt&oslash;j g&oslash;r, hvilke parametre det tager, og hvad det returnerer.
                Alle input valideres med <strong>Zod-skemaer</strong> (runtime type-tjek).
            </p>

            @* Tool details - expandable *@
            @foreach (var tool in mcpTools)
            {
                <div class="docs-tool-detail @(expandedTool == tool.Name ? "expanded" : "")"
                     @onclick="() => ToggleTool(tool.Name)">
                    <div class="docs-tool-detail-header">
                        <div>
                            <div class="docs-tool-name" style="margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">@tool.Name</div>
                            <div class="docs-tool-subtitle">@tool.Subtitle</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="docs-tool-badges">
                            @if (tool.ReadOnly)
                            {
                                <span class="docs-tag tag-file">read-only</span>
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                <span class="docs-tag tag-state">skriver filer</span>
                            }
                            @if (tool.RequiresNetwork)
                            {
                                <span class="docs-tag tag-ai">netv&aelig;rk</span>
                            }
                        </div>
                        <span class="docs-expand-icon">@(expandedTool == tool.Name ? "\u25B2" : "\u25BC")</span>
                    </div>

                    @if (expandedTool == tool.Name)
                    {
                        <div class="docs-tool-detail-body" @onclick:stopPropagation="true">
                            <div class="docs-tool-explain">@((MarkupString)tool.Description)</div>

                            <div class="docs-two-col" style="margin-top: 1rem; gap: 0.75rem;">
                                <div>
                                    <div class="docs-mini-label">Parametre (input)</div>
                                    <div class="docs-code-block" style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">
                                        <pre><code>@((MarkupString)tool.InputExample)</code></pre>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="docs-mini-label">Returnerer (output)</div>
                                    <div class="docs-code-block" style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">
                                        <pre><code>@((MarkupString)tool.OutputExample)</code></pre>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(tool.PracticalNote))
                            {
                                <div class="docs-callout" style="margin-top: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                                    @((MarkupString)tool.PracticalNote)
                                </div>
                            }
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>
            }

            @* ─── Paginering ─── *@
            <h3 class="docs-h3">Paginering &mdash; hvorfor og hvordan</h3>
            <div class="docs-explainer">
                <p>
                    En XLIFF-fil kan indeholde <strong>tusindvis</strong> af overs&aelig;ttelsesenheder. Hvis AI'en fik dem alle p&aring; &eacute;n gang,
                    ville den l&oslash;be t&oslash;r for kontekstvindue. Derfor bruger alle l&aelig;se-v&aelig;rkt&oslash;jer <code>offset</code> og <code>limit</code>:
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="docs-code-block" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
                <div class="docs-code-title">Pagineringseksempel: hent 50 ad gangen</div>
                <pre><code><span class="cc">// F&oslash;rste batch</span>
{ <span class="cf">"offset"</span>: <span class="cs">0</span>, <span class="cf">"limit"</span>: <span class="cs">50</span> }  <span class="cc">&#8594; tekst 1-50</span>

<span class="cc">// N&aelig;ste batch</span>
{ <span class="cf">"offset"</span>: <span class="cs">50</span>, <span class="cf">"limit"</span>: <span class="cs">50</span> } <span class="cc">&#8594; tekst 51-100</span>

<span class="cc">// Alle p&aring; &eacute;n gang</span>
{ <span class="cf">"offset"</span>: <span class="cs">0</span>, <span class="cf">"limit"</span>: <span class="cs">0</span> }  <span class="cc">&#8594; alle tekster</span></code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="docs-callout">
                <strong>Vigtigt:</strong> Efter at AI'en kalder <code>saveTranslatedTexts</code>, skal den nulstille paginering til <code>offset: 0</code>.
                Grunden er at listen af uoversatte tekster &aelig;ndrer sig n&aring;r overs&aelig;ttelser gemmes (og propageres), s&aring; de gamle offsets passer ikke l&aelig;ngere.
            </div>

            @* ─── Propagering ─── *@
            <h3 class="docs-h3">Propagering &mdash; den smarte genvej</h3>
            <p class="docs-section-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                N&aring;r AI'en gemmer en overs&aelig;ttelse, sker der mere end bare at &eacute;n tekst opdateres.
                <strong>Propagering</strong> betyder at alle andre steder med n&oslash;jagtig samme kildetekst automatisk f&aring;r den samme overs&aelig;ttelse.
            </p>

            <div class="docs-dataflow" style="flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: stretch;">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;">
                    <div class="docs-df-node df-blue" style="min-width: 200px;">
                        <div class="docs-df-label">AI gemmer</div>
                        <div class="docs-df-sub">"Amount" &#8594; "Bel&oslash;b"</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="docs-df-arrow">&#8594;</div>
                    <div class="docs-df-node df-purple" style="min-width: 200px;">
                        <div class="docs-df-label">saveTranslatedTexts</div>
