            <div class="docs-explainer" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                <p>
                    Propagering sker <strong>kun</strong> for status <code>translated</code>, <code>final</code> og <code>signed-off</code>.
                    Hvis AI'en s&aelig;tter status til <code>needs-review-translation</code>, propageres der <strong>ikke</strong> &mdash;
