            <h3 class="docs-h3">Praktisk eksempel: AI overs&aelig;tter en app</h3>
            <p class="docs-section-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                Her er den typiske sekvens af tool-kald n&aring;r en AI-agent overs&aelig;tter en hel app:
            </p>

            <div class="docs-sequence">
                <div class="docs-seq-step">
                    <div class="docs-seq-num">1</div>
                    <div class="docs-seq-content">
